Our group, “Cyber-Shield: Spot the Phishing Scam,” was formed with the aim of spreading awareness about cybersecurity and helping people identify phishing scams and online threats. As cyberattacks and fraudulent activities continue to increase in today’s digital world, our team is committed to educating users about safe online practices and methods to recognize suspicious emails, fake websites, and scam messages.

