Each member brings unique ideas, teamwork, and enthusiasm to the project. Together, we plan to collaborate effectively, share knowledge, and develop creative solutions to promote cybersecurity awareness. Through this project, we hope to improve our technical skills, communication, problem-solving abilities, and understanding of real-world cyber threats.

As a team, we believe that awareness is the first line of defense against phishing scams, and our mission is to help create a safer digital environment for everyone.
